snippet.title: Kingsley's Adventure trailer
snippet.description: Would you rather watch an adventure or be in one? This is the story of Kingsley, fox club and unlikely hero on a quest to save the Fruit Kingdom from the evil Wizard, Bad Custard. This is a job worthy only of a True Knight. Are you ready for the adventure of a lifetime?
